    <string name="txt_tip2">LED light bulbs use 90 percent less energy than incandescent bulbs. Switch out the most frequently used bulbs in your home with LEDs. Then, replace the rest once they burn out.</string>
    <string name="tip3">Install dimmer switches</string>
    <string name="txt_tip3">Use dimmer switches as much as possible. The key to save energy is within your reach. Switch to dimmer switches, so you only use as much light as you need</string>
